summary: Sad beginning but happy ending!
body:
Sad beginning but happy ending!

I’m going through a really rough time right now. My boyfriend and I recently broke up after 8 years together. I’m struggling to finish my thesis paper for my masters degree. Work has been stressful and I just haven’t been myself. BUT seeing @taylorswift post new music coming soon has made me smile for the first time in over 2 weeks!!!! Thank you Taylor! You always know exactly when we need you, I don’t know what I would do without you. ❤️ I can’t wait to see what you have coming for us!

summary: I feel like Taylor totally manipulates us into a false sense of security. Like, I TOTALLY bought into all the wild theories...
body: I feel like Taylor totally manipulates us into a false sense of security. Like, I TOTALLY bought into all the wild theories about new music being released/announced with the five damn holes in the fence, etc., and every time I was proved wrong. So I really did not get hyped about April the 13th because by this point I just thought it would be another theory which didn’t pan out. Do I slept in and didn’t check twitter until past midday and LOOK WHAT HAPPENED. SHE PLAYED ME LIKE THE FOOL I AM. AGAIN.
